reviewText: Bought this as a gift for a friend. He really likes it.
Very accurate, abet short description of the DVD, product shipped as stated. Very helpful for someone who used to know how to play and really needed a refresher.  Thank you.
After my two sons watched this DVD, they both took classes and are now craps dealers at local casinos.  It was motivational for them!
This DVD covers majority of craps and was very helpful. Very brief, but thorough.  Would like to see more on the dealer side of things.
